title: Dr. Gene Scott - Humorous Video Clips
description:
******************************************
DR. GENE SCOTT - HUMOROUS VIDEO CLIPS
******************************************

Until recently, many video clips of the late Dr. Gene Scott have been available on public video websites like However, Dr. Scott's widow has begun waging a quiet but intense campaign to destroy any trace of his life work from public availability.   She has sent DMCA takedown notices toand all other video sites where Dr. Scott's were to be found, and now they are no longer available.

Melissa has gone a great job of destroying Gene Scott's life work, to be sure.    Hopefully her superiors will take notice of her excellent service, and grant her promotion within The Hierarchy.

This small collection is just a handful of short clips that were posted toand other sites, consisting of some of the more outrageous and humorous outtakes from Dr. Gene Scott's lengthy career.    These are NOT serious teaching messages, which can also be downloaded via BitTorrent in MP3 format.
